				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">The 0=NTSC, 1=PAL NES, 2=Dendy scheme admits the following rules:<br /><ul><li>If non-zero, correct speeds. </li><li>If bit 0 is true, correct pitches and raster effects. </li></ul></div>

